Geislingen: more than 100 young Catholics from the small Heuberg in Firmung confirm their faith
In the two services are 101 15- and 16-year-old youth ministry unit on small Heuberg gefirmt.
The morning worship accompanied the group Laudato Si, on the afternoon of the youth choir The Spirit.
With the receipt of the Firm Sakraments the young people said yes to their baptism and enlisted the power of the Holy Spirit.
The Firmlinge had in the past few months, under the leadership of deacon Reiner Dehner and the help of many parishioners preparing for the big day.
They learned different tasks in various projects of the Christian community life and experienced Jugendtag in the Achtal line.
